%section.main
  %section.content
    = render partial: 'layouts/shared/navigation'
    = render partial: 'layouts/shared/masthead'
    %section.section-container.module-form{:style => "background-image: url(\"/assets/landing_2014/background#{(1..11).to_a.sample}.jpg\")"}
      %div.form-carousel(data-bindable="dsw-carousel" data-keyboard="false" data-activate="0")
        %div.form-carousel-inner
          - if current_user
            = simple_form_for @submission, html: { class: 'dsw-form', role: 'form' } do |f|
              %article.form-pane
                %div.form-contents
                  %div.dswacon.dswacon-bulb.dswacon-combo-primary
                  %h3.primary-heading We Want Your Ideas!
                  .p-copy
                    Denver Startup Week is a community event and is incredible because of YOUR involvement.  Submit your design, tech, business or manufacturing session idea now and help create Denver Startup Week 2014.
                  .p-copy
                    Here’s how it works:
                  .p-copy
                    Submit your session idea by <strong>May 23, 2014</strong>
                    %br
                    Complete session ideas will be voted on by the community starting <strong>June 1, 2014</strong>
                    %br
                    Winning sessions will be announced <strong>in July</strong>
                    %br
                    There is no limit to the number of ideas you may submit
                  .p-copy Questions? Comments? Concerns? Check out our #{link_to 'FAQ', '/frequently-asked-questions'}.
                %button.btn.btn-primary.form-btn.advance-btn(href="#") Get Started
              %article.form-pane
                %div.form-contents
                  %div.dswacon.dswacon-bulb.dswacon-combo-primary
                  %h3.primary-heading Submit Your Session Idea
                  .p-copy
                    Denver Startup Week is a celebration of entrepreneurship and there’s no better way to celebrate than having startups, community members and entrepreneurs throughout Downtown Denver host sessions, workshops and networking events.
                  .p-copy
                    All sessions are independently organized. Denver Startup Week organizers will help with scheduling, venues, ticketing, promotions and marketing, as well as logistics.
                  .p-copy
                    %strong Please fill out all fields as best you can. Incomplete sessions may not be presented for voting!
                  .p-copy
                    Let's start with a few basic questions:
                  = field_set_tag do
                    = f.input :format, as: :select, collection: Submission::FORMATS, prompt: 'What type of session are you proposing?', include_blank: 'Something else entirely', error: false
                    = f.input :track_id, as: :select, collection: Track.all.map { |t| [t.name, t.id]}, prompt: 'What track would it fit best into?', include_blank: 'I\'m not sure', error: false
                %button.btn.btn-primary.form-btn.advance-btn(href="#") Next
              %article.form-pane
                %div.form-contents
                  %div.dswacon.dswacon-pen.dswacon-combo-primary
                  %h3.primary-heading The Details
                  .p-copy Describe the kind of session you have in mind. What will attendees do, why they should attend, how will it impact their business, what will they learn?
                  .p-copy NOTE: This information will be displayed publicly if your session idea advances to the voting round
                  = field_set_tag do
                    = f.input :title, placeholder: 'What is your proposed title?', error: false
                    = f.input :description, placeholder: 'Describe your event. Who are your speakers/panelists (if applicable), who should attend, what will people do or learn, how does it fit into Denver Startup Week, and why is it an awesome idea?', input_html: { rows: 4 }, error: false
                %button.btn.btn-primary.form-btn.advance-btn(href="#") Next
              %article.form-pane
                %div.form-contents
                  %div.dswacon.dswacon-graph.dswacon-combo-primary
                  %h3.primary-heading Logistics
                  %div.p-copy
                    Have an idea of how many people would attend your session? Already have a location where you want to host the event? Tell us!
                    %br
                    You may leave this section blank if you don't know yet or it doesn't apply to your session.
                  = field_set_tag do
                    = f.input :location, placeholder: 'Where are you looking to hold your event?'
                    = f.input :estimated_size, placeholder: 'How many attendees can your session reasonably accomodate?'
                %button.btn.btn-primary.form-btn.advance-btn(href="#") Next
              %article.form-pane
                %div.form-contents
                  %div.dswacon.dswacon-plus.dswacon-combo-primary
                  %h3.primary-heading Building a Great Session
                  %div.p-copy How can the Denver Startup Week organizers assist in making your session the best yet?  We can assist in securing venue locations, collaborating with event partners, locating additional speakers/panel members/moderators, and even provide some financial assistance if needed.
                  = field_set_tag do
                    = f.input :notes, input_html: { rows: 4 }, placeholder: 'How can we help you build a great session?'
                %button.btn.btn-primary.form-btn.advance-btn(href="#") Next
              %article.form-pane
                %div.form-contents
                  %div.dswacon.dswacon-vote-yes.dswacon-combo-primary
                  %h3.primary-heading Confirm &amp; Submit
                  .p-copy
                    Once your idea is submitted, you will receive a confirmation email and may be contacted by a Denver Startup Week organizer if we have any questions.
                  .p-copy
                    Complete session ideas will be featured on the panel picker for community voting starting <strong>June 1</strong>
                  .p-copy
                    %strong Please confirm your e-mail address below:
                  = f.input :contact_email, placeholder: 'E-mail', error: false
                = f.button :submit, 'Submit', class: 'btn btn-primary form-btn'
          - else
            %article.form-pane
              %div.form-contents
                %div.dswacon.dswacon-bulb.dswacon-combo-primary
                %h3.primary-heading Get Started
                %div.p-copy You'll need to sign in to get going. To save you the pain of managing one more account, we use LinkedIn. 
              %a.btn.btn-primary.form-btn(href="/auth/linkedin?origin=#{new_submission_path}") Sign in with LinkedIn to continue
        %div.carousel-controls
= render partial: 'layouts/shared/footer'
= render partial: 'layouts/shared/flash_message'
= render partial: 'layouts/shared/spinner'
